        <div class="block">
            <div class="block-img-area big" data-ref="3">
                <div class="title"></div>
                <span class="name">MY CHOICE 中学</span>
                <img src="$cPath/resources/img/b5.jpg">
                <div class="overlay hide"><div class="overlay-content" style="width:253px;height:317px;"><div style="position:absolute;right:10px;bottom:4px;color:#FFFFFF">more></div><span>Xplore “MyChoice” represents our high school division, offering global partners long-term study placements for students wishing to study in England and the USA (F1). Our dedicated in-house guardianship teams provide first-rate service ensuring the very best educational and cultural study experiences.</span></div></div>
